Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:57.74,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,320)}第一話 震驚！我與姊姊是駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 原來是紀美子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在發呆看什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.37,0:03:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 姊姊是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.88,0:03:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 她是我憧憬的人 真想成為像她那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.38,0:03:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想應該不可能吧 因為我沒有才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊 實際操作才一個月耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.99,0:03:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不過是初學者 以後會越來越熟練的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本周處女座的運勢如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.36,0:04:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運日是6號 會有很棒的邂逅等著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.67,0:04:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你到底要怨歎到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五六節的機械人操作課 聽說是全校一起參與喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說新的教練也會來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快換衣服去練習吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.65,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.19,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,188 189 190 191 192 193 194
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.89,0:04:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,195 196 197 198 199 200
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跳繩明明很厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.30,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這個可以這麼棒 對機械兵器卻不行呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對機械真的很沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我同一時間 無法做兩件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要看螢幕又要動手腳 這種事我放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 看來你很有自信嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.45,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在練習跳繩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要理她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們不一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是提督的女兒 真叫人羨慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想靠關係合格嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉喔 這是實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.74,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你們也想成為駕駛員 對自己要稍微放尊重一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.91,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是高屋法子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.97,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你就是高屋提督的女兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.71,0:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是同情你的遭遇 你一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機械兵器的操縱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.29,0:06:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要同時注意6個平衡器 以及手腳的2個回傳器就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次要做這麼多事啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是怎麼操作螢幕的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…一面看一面想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.37,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在下個瞬間 該做的事情 身體就會自動幫我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 你真的是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.55,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 高屋 要達到這種地步是要努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 努力嗎？ 那你就是努力的天才囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是在駕駛機械人的 第一天就跌倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.99,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是從隔天起 我就開始練習如何不跌倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要肯努力 你也可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.33,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.77,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你的頭髮看來有點礙事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.69,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好加油吧 高屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紀美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本周處女座的運勢如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運日是6號 會有很棒的邂逅等著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.91,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶 今天是我人生中 最棒的一天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前看齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從Luxion的悲劇發生至今 已經過了6年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了對付敵人的宇宙怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.07,0:08:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各地共同進行的 RX計畫已開始了5年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 上次那個計畫 聽說隔壁男生部 派出的兩名人選好像已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊一定是 派姊姊去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但問題是 另一個人要派誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說會從全校裡選出 所以我們也有機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 若能跟憧憬的姊姊 一起上宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死也甘心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.03,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是三年級的柏原啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.64,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且聽說這次來的教練是中校呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像是為了這個計畫 特地來這裡赴任的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噓 是教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.95,0:08:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從今天開始要指導你們 操作機械兵器的太田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法跟上的人 我會毫不留情的當掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我要把大家的 自動平衡器關掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後不許再用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手動操作是實戰必要的基本能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.01,0:09:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法自己站好的傢伙 給我從學科開始重念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來去跑操場50圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喊出聲音！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.39,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？奇怪？我想想… 跑步…跑步是…這樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.51,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的一年級菜鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.15,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我從機械兵器上滾下來 用自己的腳跑操場50圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經是放學時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.03,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還待在校園裡的學生 請趕快回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法子 法子快點回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在這裡睡覺啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.71,0:10:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 我動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.35,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你死要面子 真的跑完了50圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.79,0:10:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 來吧 快點換衣服 回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（代表選出）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（天野和美、高屋法子）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（高屋法子）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.16,0:11:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.86,0:11:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說她爸爸是那個 遭到全數殲滅的艦隊提督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她是靠關係 而當上駕駛員的囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問嗎？ 她動作真的很遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天不是也看到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練真是偏心 真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天只會奉承
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸都被全滅了 竟然還想靠這種方法接近姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.21,0:11:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然得跟那個全滅女搭檔 姊姊真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.16,0:11:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對於教練在想什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對於教練在想什麼 實在搞不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子駕駛機械兵器 還不到一個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上宇宙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.54,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得同樣是三年級的 柏原會比較適合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.55,0:12:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說那孩子是 高屋提督的獨生女是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是提督所指揮的宇宙戰艦 Luxion的倖存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才找她去當駕駛員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好 這個計畫 比你想像中的更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是賭上人類存亡的難題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼為何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責人就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是她 或許辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.58,0:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Buster機組 上了宇宙你就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.25,0:12:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練是爸爸船上的倖存者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎麼辦？法子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.74,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不但被姊姊徹底的討厭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又因為爸爸的關係 當上駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被全校當成全民公敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.22,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦？ 真是倒楣到家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本周處女座的運勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.19,0:13:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心被周圍的人誤解和麻煩事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 既然都已經被選上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能好好努力 讓它能動不就好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家不要這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.12,0:14:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你 請不要再欺負我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說我選上你的那件事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會覺得我在欺負你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我根本沒有那個能力 絕對沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連一點希望也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.16,0:14:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在說你對我偏心 而且還要我跟天野學姊搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過份了 太殘忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說的只有這些嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.65,0:14:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要成為駕駛員的你 所欠缺的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.52,0:14:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天野她有是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你缺乏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊她穿著鐵木屐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天野她的確有天分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 比那個更重要 塑造出她的能力的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她自己的努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.15,0:15:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 要達到這種地步是要努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.09,0:15:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的確沒有才能 因為你根本就缺乏努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你有天分 所以才會選上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高屋 努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,磨練自己的能力 不要依靠別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.61,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好 自己用全身去感受 用頭腦去想 用心去判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在宇宙中可以依靠的 只有自己而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.12,0:15:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 與天野一起上宇宙吧 有些事你必須要去完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.77,0:17:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以為她馬上就會辭退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到她還蠻努力的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表現得不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本動作變得熟練多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.25,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是當然的 因為教練一直陪著她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會變得更加熟練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.11,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練 我哪裡比不上高屋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒必要回答你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.68,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.32,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別一副丟人樣 柏原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你升上少尉 高屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.14,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天終於要出發了 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 今天放學後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不可以給我點時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛你自己的機械兵器來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.93,0:18:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你會在出發前就放棄 沒想到你蠻努力的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.10,0:18:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你自己不放棄的話 就由我來幫你放棄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了 全滅女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.44,0:19:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離9.7 8.5 那個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是跑步就已經費盡全力的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.46,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來根本無法兼顧格鬥戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.45,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.73,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法子 你不要緊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.17,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練 不要再讓她們打了 再打下去就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.41,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法子她太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.71,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼？ 實戰可不只是這樣而已喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算其他人認同你 我可絕對不認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.72,0:20:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教練 教練 我該怎麼辦？教練…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.36,0:20:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要依靠別人 用全身去感受 用心去判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.43,0:20:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 是我不夠集中 總是特別在意監視器的畫面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,監視器關掉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她竟然做這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.35,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟…竟然沒把我放在眼裡 你這下完了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.73,0:21:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三角錐拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛…飛起來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.31,0:21:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閃電踢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.17,0:21:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛機械兵器才一個月的女孩 竟能使出閃電踢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高屋 天野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.22,0:22:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們遲早會成為前鋒遊擊 機械兵器部隊的TOP部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.33,0:22:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真正的困難從現在才要開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了成為真正的TOP部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.84,0:22:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了成為真正能夠守護人群 拯救朋友的宇宙戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.75,0:22:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄努力 要克服它 然後戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.76,0:23:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美的富士山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.73,0:23:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標成為TOP部隊是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.31,0:24:01.77,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}像妹妹一樣的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.31,0:24:01.77,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いもうと みたい そんざい だって
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.78,0:24:06.61,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你小聲地回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.78,0:24:06.61,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あなた が こたえ つぶやいた の よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.61,0:24:11.32,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}抱著必死決心的告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.61,0:24:11.32,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひっし だった こくはく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.32,0:24:15.32,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就在周日隨風而散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.32,0:24:15.32,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かぜ に ちった にちようび
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.32,0:24:19.89,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}在太陽底下被拒絕時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.32,0:24:19.89,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}たいよう の した ふられちゃう とね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.89,0:24:24.67,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}根本就輪不到淚水上場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.89,0:24:24.67,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}なみだ なんか も でばん が なくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.67,0:24:32.07,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}只能茫然的朝著你的背影揮手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.67,0:24:32.07,SongJap,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ ボーゼン と せなか に て を ふった の…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.07,0:24:34.08,SongChn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}真是沒出息
